{"tid":395376,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[肥陳冷門]然後怎樣","createTime":"2017-09-10T17:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T09:48:03.000Z","uid":45957,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90f14b0a0696668a844fba48703211f69eeb3f88","tid":395376,"uid":45957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qquxLNE_Gws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqquxLNE_Gws&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=820716e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qquxLNE_Gws</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首歌好短(但其實佢CD版係5分幾鐘有2段)<br />\n但唱到哂男人到中年既唏噓 由一個少年到中坑既茫然若失<br />\n唔單只咁 呢隻歌仲係同我的快樂時代呼應<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Eason/M.1215533119.A.93B.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FEason%2FM.1215533119.A.93B.html&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=a48c5e0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Eason/M.1215533119.A.93B.html</a><br />\n<br />\n看到&lt;然後怎樣&gt;的歌詞發現他們是相互呼應的,(兩首皆是林夕的詞)<br />\n<br />\n讓我有個美滿旅程---擁有了旅行的空檔 卻遺失了流浪的背襄<br />\n<br />\n讓我有個永遠假期---假期過完 有甚麼打算<br />\n<br />\n讓我渴睡也可嬉戲---我最初只貪玩 為何變負擔<br />\n<br />\n讓我信自己的真理---為何我的問題 總得等待別人的答案<br />\n<br />\n讓我有勇氣去喊停---不能滿足 不敢停站<br />\n<br />\n長路漫漫是如何走過---沿著軌道 一直瀏覽<br />\n<br />\n無論日夜是如何經過---走過一個天堂 少一個方向<br />\n<br />\n毫無代價唱最幸福的歌---我的快樂時代唱爛 才領悟代價多高昂<br />\n<br />\n同樣係林夕既歌 同樣係作比陳奕迅既歌 可能係想表達陳奕迅係出道10幾年後既感觸<br />\n<br />\n唔知算唔算冷門 但係呢隻歌係真係幾聽到人頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上春浪LIVE 我都係鐘意CD版多D<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Ny35VkZObo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-Ny35VkZObo&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=8c0c912d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Ny35VkZObo</a>"},{"pid":"e983d1265f8dec62bc37d0c39f77e58d4b4cc911","tid":395376,"uid":45957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩搵到CD版 雖然中間冇聲但係後尾有多段 唔同伴奏唔同感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚正 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xyhKWzNiyLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxyhKWzNiyLU&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=901b8efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xyhKWzNiyLU</a>"},{"pid":"ffa502c84978a28fa41ff0016ab8d68c1bb46a7e","tid":395376,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:05:14.000Z","msg":"讀asso聽到上返u<br />\n仲有首路一直都在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ded4832ec78db39ff7a1acb089e226a3b3c328","tid":395376,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"睇錯不如這樣"},{"pid":"a5eedb1a7a2418f877f7debe6418b19add9600f9","tid":395376,"uid":45957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀asso聽到上返u<br />\n仲有首路一直都在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不想放手同上五樓的快活絕對係eason既國語癲峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6ea8c67b8f0f964f3f02242a3f7dd749c1c61b","tid":395376,"uid":45957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯不如這樣</blockquote><br />\n都係值得推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呢首算冷門咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb437c4da7561205d49d6ed2e418559a2b8013ca","tid":395376,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:22:33.000Z","msg":"我都好鍾意呢首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid